BackType,is,a,service,that,lets,you,find,follow,and,share,comments,from,across,the,web,The,BackType,API,allows,you,to,develop,applications,that,leverage,their,dataset,and,interact,with,their,website,The,way,that,BackType,works,is,that,when,a,Web,user,fills,out,the,Website,or,URL,box,in,a,comment,form,on,someone,s,blog,BackType,assigns,it,to,that,person,Then,that,commenter,has,a,BackType,profile,that,includes,the,comments,they,ve,posted,on,the,Web